{"tid":1586972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]連登最大休閒抗爭PO上線啦(9.22)","createTime":"2019-09-22T08:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T14:07:30.000Z","uid":235465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"09ab5e2ab6d096d9a3ba31266d8a700615019482","tid":1586972,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:18:48.000Z","msg":"[頭先個po犯左個幾嚴重錯誤 重開]<br />\n覺得遊行太遠太麻煩?<br />\n覺得勇武太暴力太高風險?<br />\n覺得和你拖無女女肯同你拖唔去?<br />\n覺得自己咩都做唔到?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔緊要 我地幫到你<br />\n唔使圍狗屋 唔使遊行 唔使拖手<br />\n簡簡單單 在家或落街行兩步就完成 極低風險<br />\n<br />\n正經:本po為長期整合一D線上活動 例如眾籌 聯署 或一D twitter上活動<br />\n但本po內全部活動相對輕便 不包括遊行 和你拖 和你塞等等等等主流活動<br />\n而通常本po會分 主要/次要 主要則代表發起後有迫切性去做 或重要度較高<br />\n眾籌 聯署方面 可能隨時更新 請善用追故模式<br />\n<br />\n主要<br />\n<br />\n1.twitter戰線- #birdfoldingchallenge<br />\nlink:<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EnzoMazak/status/1174409465489027072?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEnzoMazak%2Fstatus%2F1174409465489027072%3Fs%3D09&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2Fctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=7ee3d9d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEnzoMazak%2Fstatus%2F1174409465489027072%3Fs%3D09&h=fcbcba01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EnzoMazak/status/1174409465489027072?s=09</a><br />\n日期:即日起<br />\n時間:無時間限制<br />\n內容:摺一隻紙鶴 放上twitter 再tag #929GlobalAntiChinazi 同#birdfoldingchallenge<br />\n<br />\n2.twitter-facebook 戰線-支持人權法案<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1174703441022783489?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1174703441022783489%3Fs%3D09&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2Fctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=56aecc67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1174703441022783489%3Fs%3D09&h=b09d6829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1174703441022783489?s=09</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3341501159208558&amp;id=178910518800987\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3341501159208558%26id%3D178910518800987&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2Fctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=de782f3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3341501159208558&amp;id=178910518800987</a><br />\n日期:即日起<br />\n時間:無時間限制<br />\n內容:retweet rubio個post like facebook個po<br />\n<br />\n3.和你貼-復修連儂牆<br />\n日期:9月22後<br />\n地點:各地連儂牆<br />\n內容:復修各地連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n4:反暴文宣-向白衣暴徒說不<br />\n日期:9月21後<br />\n內容:到twitter retweet 白衣暴徒打人片段 令外界知道勇武單純自衛<br />\n<br />\n次要:<br />\n<br />\n1:10 點大叫<br />\n時間:10點<br />\n內容:大叫<br />\n地點:你鐘意"},{"pid":"54dd74f309dfdf21eb3a0e80457ee90b6e845fdf","tid":1586972,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b78df611acd736fd7e9da68fa3cad56789771071","tid":1586972,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42063e453d7d57be6b74235f28ebbed0226b764d","tid":1586972,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6baad11066ff2b3b0266a4e119411a337f3ebf7","tid":1586972,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:20:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行動